title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 79: Round 2 Preview
description:
On a special Thursday episode, the guys recap the epic Game 7 in Boston Wednesday night between the Bruins and Leafs. RA gives his take on what it was like inside the barn while Biz and Whits tell us what they saw watching at home. They break down why the Bs are moving on and the Leafs are all done. Lots of adrenaline still flowing for this one. The fellas then get everyone up to speed on the Conference Semi-Final match-ups and give their picks.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
